\( \boldsymbol{\vec{y}^{\,\prime}}(t) = A \boldsymbol{\vec{y}}(t) \),
where \( A \) is a real \( 2 \times 2 \) constant matrix with
repeated eigenvalues.  Use the given information to determine
the matrix \( A \).
$PAR
